===Cardinal Number===
'''yhdeksän'''

#[[nine]]

===Etymology===
A compound of yh- and deksän. The former comes from [[yksi]], while the latter is from the same common Indo-European root ''*dek-'' as e.g. Latin [[decem]] and Hungarian [[tíz]]. So the compound originally meant one (from) ten.

